strings: <voice_0x010018DB><se_high>Accuracy: Alexandra... bless us and protect us to the end.
<voice_0x010018DC><se_high>Accuracy: I can't believe what has happened since I met you and everyone else here.
<voice_0x010018DD><se_high>Accuracy: At first I didn't understand the term. You are easily offended and always seem to listen to other people's opinions.
<voice_0x010018DE><se_high>Accuracy: But when you save me from the hunter's curse I began to see you in a different light
<voice_0x010018E0><se_high>Accuracy: The more time we spent together, the more our relationship grew. Until you realize that I love you.
<voice_0x010018E1><se_high>Accuracy: haha a lot of things like last year
<voice_0x010018E2><se_high>Accuracy: I'll take the house home anyway
